M||tx|---
M||titl|Initialize App Once, Not Per Mount
M||impa|lo-md
M||impa|avoids duplicate init in dv
M||tags|initialization, useEffect, app-startup, side-effects
M||tx|---
M|Init|tx|Do not put app-wide initialization that must run once per app load inside `useEffect([])` of a cp. cp can remount and effects will re-run. Use a md-level guard or top-level init in the entry md instead.
M|Init|**In|**
M|Init|tx|```tsx
M|Init|tx|fn Comp() {
M|Init|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Init|tx|loadFromStorage()
M|Init|tx|checkAuthToken()
M|Init|tx|}, [])
M|Init|tx|// ...
M|Init|tx|}
M|Init|tx|```
M|Init|**Co|**
M|Init|tx|```tsx
M|Init|tx|let didInit = false
M|Init|tx|fn Comp() {
M|Init|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Init|tx|if (didInit) return
M|Init|tx|didInit = true
M|Init|tx|loadFromStorage()
M|Init|tx|checkAuthToken()
M|Init|tx|}, [])
M|Init|tx|// ...
M|Init|tx|}
M|Init|tx|```
M|Init|Refe|[Initializing the application](https://rc.dv/learn/you-might-not-need-an-effect#initializing-the-application)